title: 00850 : 20V ~.60A draw, no display, no plug in chime, hot CPU
message:
Multiple liquid damage points. Near R8711 ssd 1v8 power was especially bad.  Replaced and tested nearly everything in that section.

Also found damage on cc805 and cc804 pins 1 pads were missing completely.  Replaced and reattached with magnet wire.  Nervous about that since it's CPU power related.  I'm new to these boards so apologies if I missed important values.
